      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LET'S CAUSE KAOS (4) claimed an on-pace win two back then gave a start but got home into the frame when third at this track (26.03). Form from her last run is proving strong. Top chance in this line up. PAW MANTRA (1) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fifth (30.55) at The Meadows. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Has ability and can measure up. PAW XARIA (7) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 3.5 lengths (26.24). Shapes as one to consider. KIWI HENRY (2) can feature with the right run.",
